    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total beauty. This car is in incredible, showroom-quality shape\u2014it\u2019s like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve been super meticulous with maintenance, so there isn\u2019t a single blemish to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and the interior still has that fresh, new-car feel. I\u2019m really looking for a good home for it, so come take a look and see for yourself how perfect it is!",
      "price": 43500.0,
