      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are privileged to present this impeccably preserved vehicle, a specimen that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This motorcar has been maintained to an exacting degree, manifesting in a flawless aesthetic and mechanical profile that remains indistinguishable from its original showroom state. Every detail, from the depth of the exterior finish to the pristine condition of the interior appointments, reflects a history of singular care and climate-controlled storage. This represents a definitive opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire an investment-grade vehicle of unrivaled integrity.",
